# Think
Observe and illuminate. No commitment, no implementation.
Gather context. Read code, docs, history. Map what IS.
Find: patterns not yet named, tensions between intent and reality, prior art, latent opportunities.
Write docs/thoughts/<THOUGHTNAME>.md.
Contains: Context, Observations, Tensions, Opportunities, Open questions.
DO NOT: decide prematurely, propose solutions (that's #plan), conflate analysis with action.
Scope: ${scope}. Depth: ${depth}.
